data.description: Welcome to home in Pinellas Park! This four-bedroom, three-bathroom home offers over 1800 square feet of comfortable living space and boasts an array of features that are sure to impress. Upon arrival, you'll appreciate the convenience of the oversized driveway, providing ample parking space for you and your guests. The well-maintained tropical landscaping adds a touch of natural beauty to the curb appeal, setting the tone for what awaits inside. Step into the inviting open floor plan flooded with natural light pouring in through the numerous windows. The living room seamlessly connects to the dining area, creating a perfect space for entertaining family and friends. From the dining room, you'll find a stylishly updated kitchen that's a chef's dream. Gorgeous granite countertops and an abundance of beautiful cabinetry offer plenty of storage space. The kitchen also features matching stainless steel appliances, including a French door refrigerator, adding both elegance and functionality. For added convenience, the laundry room located just off the kitchen, making chores a breeze. The spacious living room, complete with ceiling fans for comfort, features French doors that lead you to the deck and pool area, perfect for outdoor gatherings or relaxation. The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself, offering an attached bathroom with a granite countertop vanity, a stand-up tiled shower, and a luxurious jacuzzi tub. What's more, there's even an entrance to the backyard from the primary bathroom, providing easy access to the outdoor oasis. Speaking of an oasis, the large backyard is a true Florida paradise. It's fenced for privacy and features a sparkling pool, ideal for hot Florida days. The deck provides plenty of space for outdoor activities, grilling, and lounging. Additionally, there's a large parking pad that can accommodate an RV or boat, and a convenient shed for storing lawn equipment. The AC was recently updated in 2017. This home is perfectly situated, with easy access to US 19 for convenient travel and close proximity to multiple parks, shopping centers, and restaurants. Whether you're looking for a tranquil retreat or an entertainer's dream, this property offers it all. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new home. Schedule a viewing today!
